<div id='rsvp-notifications' class='hidden'>
  <button id='close-notifications' type="button" class="close" aria-label="Close">
    <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
  </button>
  <div class='content' />
</div>
<h1 class="text-center col-md-12">RSVP</h1>
<p>
Thank you for RSVPing! Please select which of the guests on your invitation below will
be joining us for the wedding on the 25th, and which cannot make it. If you need to change your response,
you can do so before June 20th. Thanks!
</p>
<p>
We would also like to extend an invitation for all guests who are in town to join us at the
<a href="/friday">rehearsal dinner</a> on the night of Friday, July 24th. There is a section
below to RSVP for that as well, and we would greatly appreciate it if you could let us know which members
of your party will be able to attend.
</p>
<p>
Also, feel free to leave us a comment. At a moment, those are private, so Amanda and I are the only ones who
can read them. We will make sure to ask for permission before sharing any touching messages we receive.
</p>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6">
  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h3 class="panel-title">RSVP for the Wedding - July 25th</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      {{#each guests}}
      <div class="rsvp-wedding">
        <div class="btn-group rsvp-group" data-toggle="buttons">
          {{#if rsvp}}
            {{#if attending}}
              <label class="btn btn-primary rsvp-yes active" data-id="{{id}}">
                <input type="radio" name="rsvp-response" autocomplete="off" checked> Attending
              </label>
              <label class="btn btn-primary rsvp-no" data-id="{{id}}">
                <input type="radio" name="rsvp-response" autocomplete="off"> Not Attending
              </label>
            {{else}}
              <label class="btn btn-primary rsvp-yes" data-id="{{id}}">
                <input type="radio" name="rsvp-response" autocomplete="off"> Attending
              </label>
              <label class="btn btn-primary rsvp-no active" data-id="{{id}}">
                <input type="radio" name="rsvp-response" autocomplete="off" checked> Not Attending
              </label>
            {{/if}}
          {{else}}
            <label class="btn btn-primary rsvp-yes" data-id="{{id}}">
              <input type="radio" name="rsvp-response" autocomplete="off"> Attending
            </label>
            <label class="btn btn-primary rsvp-no" data-id="{{id}}">
              <input type="radio" name="rsvp-response" autocomplete="off" checked> Not Attending
            </label>
          {{/if}}
        </div>
        <div class='guest-name'>{{this.fullName}}</div>
        <div class='clearfix'/>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h3 class="panel-title">RSVP for the Rehearsal Dinner - July 24th</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      {{#each guests}}
      <div class="rsvp-rehearsal">
        <div class="btn-group rsvp-group" data-toggle="buttons">
          {{#if rsvp}}
            {{#if attendingRehearsal}}
            <label class="btn btn-primary rsvp-rehearsal-yes active" data-id="{{id}}">
              <input type="radio" name="rsvp-rehearsal-response" autocomplete="off" checked> Attending
            </label>
            <label class="btn btn-primary rsvp-rehearsal-no" data-id="{{id}}">
              <input type="radio" name="rsvp-rehearsal-response" autocomplete="off"> Not Attending
            </label>
            {{else}}
            <label class="btn btn-primary rsvp-rehearsal-yes" data-id="{{id}}">
              <input type="radio" name="rsvp-rehearsal-response" autocomplete="off"> Attending
            </label>
            <label class="btn btn-primary rsvp-rehearsal-no active" data-id="{{id}}">
              <input type="radio" name="rsvp-rehearsal-response" autocomplete="off" checked> Not Attending
            </label>
            {{/if}}
          {{else}}
            <label class="btn btn-primary rsvp-rehearsal-yes" data-id="{{id}}">
              <input type="radio" name="rsvp-rehearsal-response" autocomplete="off"> Attending
            </label>
            <label class="btn btn-primary rsvp-rehearsal-no" data-id="{{id}}">
              <input type="radio" name="rsvp-rehearsal-response" autocomplete="off" checked> Not Attending
            </label>
          {{/if}}
        </div>
        <div class='guest-name'>{{this.fullName}}</div>
        <div class='clearfix'/>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <h4 class="panel-title">Comments</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p></p>
        <form id="comment-form" class="comment">
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-12">
                <label for="comment">If you'd like to leave us a comment, please do so here!</label>
                <textarea id="comment" name="comment" class="form-control" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-10">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Submit</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
